{"tid":1534733,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"9月7日 機場壓力測試2.0！","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T15:23:39.000Z","uid":97330,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"07881e2994ffa5fd4b32dde854bbc3dd1813ed3f","tid":1534733,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:58:11.000Z","msg":"成個熱門都無乜行動post！<br />\n求下大家，我唔係啲咩有影響力既人<br />\n但我知只要每個人開一個post<br />\n就多分一機會，機場真係唯一可以撼動到香港經濟地位既方法<br />\n啲人又唔敢真正起義，咁唯一有威脅力既就得返機場<br />\n<br />\n約定你地<br />\n<br />\n9月7日<br />\n機場壓力測試2.0！"},{"pid":"3df57491d64e14a8b594b6bf079fd9f953196fa4","tid":1534733,"uid":123991,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:58:22.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3bfeaa639cb0ba6e57fbe44b087d63128faaf0a","tid":1534733,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:58:40.000Z","msg":"自推X10 10/10"},{"pid":"4778fc9f8b72126f858bd6003bcba5d17b75a0ca","tid":1534733,"uid":143699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:58:42.000Z","msg":"大家真係冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上太子站黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘<br />\n<br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映錯誤示範</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBkjO1B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBkjO1B.gif&h=c106dd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位狗狗好明顯冇睇教學片啦，大家千奇唔好學佢啊，動作要標準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n-最近黨鐵多咗狗，如果情況唔允許，希望大家都唔好勉強，可以改用老人卡。唔好因為咁而被人捉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完整示範片段：\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFDYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=e604cf11\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"2cc9d2d59979529ca656d7c7fe7b4b604e9d7fa6","tid":1534733,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3df57491d64e14a8b594b6bf079fd9f953196fa4","tid":1534733,"uid":123991,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:58:22.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:58:51.000Z","msg":"快撚到，勁"},{"pid":"520b3177efe40fcc638a6432ba264d914418c4ef","tid":1534733,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:59:04.000Z","msg":"自推X10 ９/10"},{"pid":"a13d5c5689e920dcc355586151a5bb8a4e548247","tid":1534733,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:59:16.000Z","msg":"自推X10 8/10"},{"pid":"839bc32ffac038fbcd08feb898d474bb81d63c8b","tid":1534733,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:59:28.000Z","msg":"自推X10 7/10"},{"pid":"43e499dbd630b542d61648e1702569356138f3eb","tid":1534733,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-0